Package com.ibm.mq.explorer.ms0s.mqsceditor

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MQSCActionContributor
    This sets up the default ActionContributor.
    MQSCAnnotationHover
    This implements an IAnnotationHover that provides some additional logging when the plugin is in debug mode.
    MQSCDocumentSetupParticipant
    This implements an IDocumentSetupParticipant to connect various parts of the plugin to the Eclipse runtime editor framework.
    MQSCEditor
    This is the main TextEditor class.
    MQSCEditorMessages
    This loads any messages from the resource bundle for the plugin.
    MQSCEditorPlugin
    This extends AbstractUIPlugin to provide the main plugin class.
    MQSCPartitionScanner
    This creates a RuleBasedPartitionScanner to identify the individual MQSC Commands in an MQSC document.
    MQSCPresentationAction
    This creates a TextEditorAction to configure and execute presentation options.
    MQSCSourceViewerConfiguration
    This extends SourceViewerConfiguration to provide the necessary methods for the SourceViewer to access the objects it needs.
    MQSCTextHover
    This enables hover text.
